@startuml
title YPS Publish to Queue and Sale Service Consume & Print

|YPS / External Caller|
start
:Send pushMoney request;

|YPS Entry Service|
:Receive request;
:Validate signature and required fields;
:Validate bill / product / store / charging rule;
:Prepare sale payload;
:Save request log / outbox (optional);
:Publish sale message to RabbitMQ;

|RabbitMQ|
:Queue sale message;

|Sale Service|
:Consume sale message;
:Check idempotency / duplicate request;

if (Duplicate?) then (Yes)
  :Skip processing;
  stop
else (No)
  :Prepare sale transaction;
endif

|Database|
:Save sale_transaction;
:Save commission_transaction;
:Save print_summary / audit log;

|Sale Service|
:Prepare print payload;

|Printer / Print Module|
:Print voucher;

|Sale Service|
:Update processing status = SUCCESS;
stop
@enduml
